OL,3,CInadequate care provision 'contributed
OL,4,Cto death of girl in hospital grounds'
OL,6,FAn "inadequate" provision of mental
OL,7,Fhealth beds and "poor communication"
OL,8,Fcontributed to the death of a teenage
OL,9,Fgirl on hospital grounds, an inquest
OL,10,Fhas found.
OL,12,FEllame Ford-Dunn, 16, died after
OL,13,Fabsconding in the grounds of Worthing
OL,14,FHospital while she was a mental health
OL,15,Finpatient on March 20 2022.
OL,17,FShe had absconded "multiple times"
OL,18,Fduring her stay on Bluefin ward at
OL,19,FWorthing Hospital, which was not a
OL,20,Fspecialist mental health ward.
