OL,6,FAt West Sussex coroner's court in
OL,7,FHorsham on Monday, jurors concluded
OL,8,Fthe decision to place Ellame on
OL,9,FBluefin ward was "inappropriate" and
OL,10,F"more than minimally" contributed to
OL,11,Fher death.
OL,13,FHer parents Ken and Nancy Ford-Dunn
OL,14,Ffelt the jury came to the right
OL,15,Fconclusions and described their
OL,16,F"devastation" at losing Ellame and
OL,17,F"anger" at the healthcare services
OL,18,Fthat failed their daughter.
