OL,6,FMrs Ford-Dunn said: "I can't brush her
OL,7,Fhair and paint her nails and wash her
OL,8,Fclothes, I can't do all those
OL,9,Fparenting things that I want to be
OL,10,Fable to do, so all we've got left is
OL,11,Fthis fight to make sure that everyone
OL,12,Funderstands how badly she was failed."
OL,14,FThe jury found: "It was inappropriate
OL,15,Ffor Ellame to be detained on a
OL,16,Fpaediatric ward from February 28 to
OL,17,FMarch 20 2022 and the risk assessments
OL,18,Fin place were inadequate and
OL,19,Finconsistently applied.
