OL,6,F"When Ellame absconded from the ward
OL,7,Fon March 20, she was not immediately
OL,8,Ffollowed by staff and it took 59
OL,9,Fminutes for her to be found by police.
OL,11,FThe decision to detain Ellame on the
OL,12,Fward without the "provision of
OL,13,Fsecurity" was also found to have
OL,14,Fcontributed to her death.
OL,16,FShe was staying in Bluefin, an acute
OL,17,Fpaediatric ward, due to a lack of
OL,18,Fprovision of available specialist
OL,19,Fmental health beds, the inquest heard.
