OL,6,FHer mental health care was provided by
OL,7,FSussex Partnership NHS Foundation
OL,8,FTrust (SPFT) while Bluefin Ward was
OL,9,Frun by University Hospitals Sussex NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust (UHST).
OL,12,FJurors concluded that "poor co-
OL,13,Fordination, communication and
OL,14,Faccountability" between "multiple
OL,15,Fagencies" also contributed to Ellame's
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,18,FThey also found that the
OL,19,F"inconsistency in nursing handovers"
OL,20,Fand lack of guidance for staff played
OL,21,Fa role in Ellame's death.
