OL,6,FThe jury foreman said: "The
OL,7,Finstructions given to agency-
OL,8,Fregistered mental health nurses were
OL,9,Finadequate, patient notes were held on
OL,10,Fmultiple systems, with access not
OL,11,Ffreely available to agency staff and
OL,12,Finadequately transferred during
OL,13,Fhandover.
OL,15,F"UHST's policy for missing patients
OL,16,Fwas not designed for high-risk mental
OL,17,Fhealth patients, and the procedure to
OL,18,Fbe followed in the event of absconsion
OL,19,Fwas unclear and not appropriately
OL,20,Fcommunicated."
OL,26,@nD@XOUwD@AOU|D@NO]
