OL,6,FEllame's mother told jurors they did
OL,7,Fnot feel "properly supported" by
OL,8,Fsocial services and healthcare
OL,9,Fproviders. Ms Ford-Dunn said her
OL,10,Fdaughter began to struggle with her
OL,11,Fmental health when she started
OL,12,Fsecondary school and was diagnosed
OL,13,Fwith autism, ADHD and dyslexia.
OL,15,FShe had been an inpatient on mental
OL,16,Fhealth wards before but was released
OL,17,Fin January 2022 to live with her
OL,18,Fparents, the inquest heard.
