OL,6,FOn Monday, her father Ken Ford-Dunn
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's hard to explain because
OL,8,Fyou have the devastation, you have the
OL,9,Foverwhelming, it's almost like fear of
OL,10,Fthe sadness, that personally I can't
OL,11,Fquite connect with because I've got so
OL,12,Fmuch anger towards the services that
OL,13,Ffailed her.
OL,15,FSo much."In November last year, UHST
OL,16,Fwas fined #200,000 after admitting
OL,17,Ffailing to provide safe care and
OL,18,Ftreatment to Ellame which exposed her
OL,19,Fto a significant risk of "avoidable
OL,20,Fharm".
