OL,6,FUHST says it has "fundamentally
OL,7,Fimproved" its care since Ellame's
OL,8,Fdeath.
OL,10,FDr Maggie Davies, chief nurse for
OL,11,FUHST, said: "The loss of Ellame at
OL,12,Fsuch a young age was a tragedy and
OL,13,Fdevastating for everyone who knew and
OL,14,Floved her.
OL,16,F"We had a responsibility to protect
OL,17,Fher while she was in our care and we
OL,18,Fare deeply sorry that we were not able
OL,19,Fto do so.
