OL,6,F"Dr Richard Sankar, clinical director
OL,7,Ffor the NHS-led Hampshire, Isle of
OL,8,FWight, Sussex, Kent and Medway Child
OL,9,Fand Adolescent Mental Health Services
OL,10,F(CAMHS) Provider Collaborative, said:
OL,11,F"We offer our sincere condolences to
OL,12,FEllame's family. We acknowledge the
OL,13,Fdelay in identifying a mental health
OL,14,Fbed for Ellame.
OL,16,F"Our aim is always to provide people
OL,17,Fwith care that both meets a person's
OL,18,Findividual needs and is as close as
OL,19,Fpossible to their family and
OL,20,Fcommunity."
