OL,6,FArea coroner Joanne Andrews also
OL,7,Fordered a prevention of future deaths
OL,8,Freport from NHS England after hearing
OL,9,Fevidence that a "number" of young
OL,10,Fpeople continue to be held on acute
OL,11,Fpaediatric wards like Bluefin, while
OL,12,Fwaiting for an acute mental health
OL,13,Fward bed to become available.
OL,15,FThe coroner has also requested
OL,16,Fevidence from both trusts about
OL,17,Fimprovements they have implemented to
OL,18,Ftheir communication and report sharing
OL,19,Fsystems.NHS England has been contacted
OL,20,Ffor comment.
